Please check this sheet [mailboxes\_testing](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1b9knpf2RgS7NaZII1Kj8yj_1j-myncwbBdsM0L7hXck/edit?usp=sharing)

Step1: Copy your mail id and password and log into [mail.cazehiresense.com](http://mail.cazehiresense.com)  
Step2: On the top right click on the spanner button (Settings button)  
![][image1]  
Step3: Click on the app passwords and click on the create app password button  
![][image2]  
Step4: Write app name as hiresense and under password click on generate  
![][image3]  
Step5: For allowed protocols for app password only enable **IMAP** and **SMTP**  
Step5: Copy the password generated and click on add  
Step6: Add the copied password to the sheet under the respective app\_password column
